init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The mugs are actually a way for the government to keep track of the population.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The worst dad is forced to go on the run.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He finally makes it to Mexico and is able to relax.
